Full Description: Buydealz is a User-driven Social Networking Cloud deal sharing site with an objective to focus on consumers’ needs bringing a platform to mingle and share information to give a great shopping experience. Comparing across products, prices, and storing information and helps to quickly access all the ratings and reviews you need to make a confident buying decision.  Using Buydealz shoppers can find the right product, at the right price, every time.  We connect customers by offering an experience to follow one another in real time with their shopping destiny. Through following the members profile and sharing the information with people interested in their products and services they intend to grow their network. This helps users to gather real-time market intelligence and feedback, and build relationships between customers, merchants and influencers. In adding administration area users can add new coupons, deals or events, organizing their products information and much more. Users can post and sell virtually anything through our site from books to electronics.  Buydealz introduces a new Deal Comparison Tool (BDCT), helps users to search more than 150 Merchants with real time product attributes in no time. It filters users search in all Product attributes including the name/title of a product, the description, an image link, a condition (new/used/refurbished), a product code like a UPC, EAN, or ISBN, a category, the brand and manufacturer, It guarantees users to choose their product with lowest total price including Tax + Shipping charge from set of selected products from merchant. Buydealz provides more merchant data and best deal than other deal comparison. Each product that is included in user search consists of one year graph with details and product reviews. Buydealz adopts Cloud computing technology as it is definitely the wave of the future. The flexibility of the Buydealz site is to respond quickly to changing needs makes it a very economically viable business computing choice. Buydealz  will be Managed Service Provider (MSP) looking at hosting and managing Customers and Advertisers own managed backup service. The advantage to any cloud computing solution is that IT is centrally located. Traditionally, IT has to be all over company grounds putting out fires and going to individual work stations that are having issues.  Buydealz offers cloud service that upgrades all deal, coupons and event that are only need to be done at one location and, as needs change, only one place gets the change. Our system can also handle as many users come on board, more memory and processor speed can be increased through our cloud services.

Description: Team Chrissy is a not-for-profit organization dedicated to helping people with multiple sclerosis.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Chicago Area, Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: Team Chrissy, NFP, is a 501(c)(3) not for profit Foundation dedicated to helping individuals and their families in Chicagoland who are dealing with Multiple Sclerosis on a daily basis.  The roots of Team Chrissy go back to the Spring of 2005 when a small group of family and friends gathered together at the MS Walk in Chicago in support of Christina Bober who was newly diagnosed with Multiple Sclerosis at the age of 22.  Christina, or “Chrissy” as she likes to be called, now 28, has since gone through many ups and downs, most of the time struggling through normal every day activities as she contends with her affliction. She has been diagnosed with secondary progressive MS and currently has a team of doctors that provide treatment at both the University of Chicago Hospital and the Cleveland Clinic. Throughout her struggle Chrissy has been able to persevere. She successfully completed a Doctor of Pharmacy Degree (PharmD) at Midwestern University in Downers Grove, Illinois in 2009 and currently works at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois as a pharmacist.  Through word of mouth, Team Chrissy has since grown to more than 100 people – family, friends and new acquaintances – each helping in their own way. Through their efforts Team Chrissy has been able to raise over $20,000.00 to benefit the National Multiple Sclerosis Society. This has been accomplished through MS charity walks, participation in MS charity softball tournaments and newly launched in 2010, an annual Team Chrissy Golf Outing.  Team Chrissy has decided to re-focus its efforts in a new direction and in February, 2011, Team Chrissy officially became Team Chrissy, NFP, a not for profit 501(c)(3) foundation. Now Team Chrissy is taking on a different responsibility for MS. This decision was made after seeing the struggles that Chrissy has gone through both physically and financially.
Industry Groups: Community and Lifestyle, Health Care, Other, Social Impact

Full Description: Nearly 400,000* Americans are living with multiple sclerosis (MS). The only common thread is that MS is a progressive disease that silently advances. While there's no cure for MS, there is good news. Today the medical community has more knowledge about MS and more medications for treating it than ever before. TYSABRI (natalizumab) increases the risk of PML. For adults with relapsing forms of Multiple Sclerosis (MS). TYSABRI (natalizumab) increases the risk of PML. When starting and continuing treatment with TYSABRI, it is important that you discuss with your doctor whether the expected benefit of TYSABRI is enough to outweigh this risk. TYSABRI is usually taken by someone who has seen their physical disability worsen or who hasn't seen the results they'd hoped for with another therapy. And, unlike daily or weekly medications, TYSABRI is given every 4 weeks as an infusion.
